{"type":null,"faqId":46152,"title":"有用户反馈摄像头前置时拍的照片左右反了怎么办？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.s2{font-family:Arial;}\n.p1{margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">前置摄像头（</span><span class=\"s2\">前置和后置用同一个摄像头</span><span class=\"s1\">，手动扳动摄像头自动打开前置摄像）拍照设置中有一项“自拍镜像”，默认是勾选的。如果勾选了此项，会把照片左右反过来，使得照片和预览画面一致。如果您想要保存真实的场景，请把“自拍镜像”取消。但是前置预览的时候始终保持镜像效果，不受镜像开关影响，这样用户看到的场景与实际效果一致，更符合用户使用习惯；目前所有手机都是这么处理的。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1086,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"1932","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Camera-Gallery","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1444376112000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":14,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"前置、相片","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}